cwn_entry.cwn_what:
Thomas also prototyped a searchable version for the CUFP Mirage tutorial: e.g.: http://www.ocamlpro.com/mirage/xen/ ;
but the search view does need some optimisation with a large number of modules, as in the standard library. The new version he's doing in HTML is far slicker and faster.
Citrix have a really useful JSON output to ocamldoc in the XAPI tree that is very handy for anyone else who wants to do something like this: https://github.com/xen-org/xen-api/blob/master/ocaml/doc/odoc_json.ml
